    <!-- Static SEO Content: visible to crawlers before JS loads -->
    <div id="seo-content" style="max-width: 64rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #3d3529; line-height: 1.6;">
      <noscript>
        <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">TimelessHome.ai &mdash; AI Interior Design & Virtual Home Staging</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Transform any room or stage an entire home with AI-powered design. Upload photos and receive professionally designed concepts with real, shoppable products.</p>
        <p>Please enable JavaScript to use the TimelessHome.ai application.</p>
      </noscript>

      <article itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage" style="display: block;">
        <header>
          <h1 itemprop="name" style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI Interior Design & Virtual Home Staging</h1>
          <p itemprop="description" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #6b5f52; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Redesign any room or virtually stage your entire home with AI. Get unique design concepts with curated shopping lists of real products, photorealistic visualizations, and room treatments &mdash; perfect for homeowners, real estate agents, and house flippers.</p>
        </header>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;">How It Works</h2>
          <ol style="padding-left: 1.25rem;">
            <li><strong>Upload a Photo</strong> &mdash; Take a photo of any room you want to redesign</li>
            <li><strong>Answer Style Questions</strong> &mdash; Tell us your preferences, budget, and vision</li>
            <li><strong>View Designs</strong> &mdash; View unique AI-generated design concepts</li>
            <li><strong>Shop the Look</strong> &mdash; Every item is real and shoppable from top retailers</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;">Three Ways to Design</h2>
          <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem; list-style: disc;">
            <li><strong>The Timeless Method</strong> &mdash; Fully automated AI pipeline. Upload, answer questions, and receive complete designs with shopping lists.</li>
            <li><strong>Interactive Design</strong> &mdash; Hands-on creative control. Choose what stays, customize styles, and shop item-by-item with AI assistance.</li>
            <li><strong>Virtual Home Staging</strong> &mdash; Stage every room in a property at once. Just provide a listing address and our AI furnishes and designs each room with photorealistic results. Ideal for real estate agents, house flippers, and property managers.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;">Every Design Includes</h2>
          <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem; list-style: disc;">
            <li>Photorealistic room visualization showing your space transformed</li>
            <li>Curated shopping list with products from eBay, Wayfair, Amazon, and more</li>
            <li>Room treatment recommendations (paint colors, flooring, wallpaper)</li>
            <li>Before-and-after comparisons</li>
            <li>Downloadable design images</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </article>
